IANA Character Sets registry

This package uses charset names and aliases from the IANA Character Sets registry as compatibility
references for accepted encoding labels. The registry is used as a reference only: this package does
not copy or derive runtime table data, registry rows, registry contact data, or registry text from
the IANA registry.

Source: https://www.iana.org/assignments/character-sets/character-sets.xhtml
Registry last updated by IANA at the time of this audit: 2024-06-06.
